steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
When I navigate to menu "Mobile app" with submenu "Mobile Editor"
Then I should see Mobile screen display
When I select tab name Pages with index 1
When I add new screen with name JIT019PreviewCode
Then I should see the screen with name JIT019PreviewCode display in list Pages
When I select screen with name JIT019PreviewCode
When I open Search popup on item value "Page" with index "1"
When I add item "View" without inputting in Search popup to preview mobile editor
When I open preview code with component mode
Then I should see the code contains "<View style={styles.view_1} />"
When I close preview code panel
When I toggle on item value "Page" with index "1"
When I select item value "View" with index "1"
When I toggle off Layout tree header
When I update field label "Width" of header "Basic" with radio "%" and value "100"
When I update field label "Height" of header "Basic" with radio "PX" and value "300"
When I update field label "Flex" of header "Basic" with value "0.5"
When I select the color for field label "Background Color" of header "Basic" by inputting the hexcode value "FF0000"
When I select the color for field label "Border Color" of header "Basic" by inputting the hexcode value "0007FF"
When I update field label "Radius" of header "Basic" with radio "PX" and value "20"
When I update field label "Border Width" of header "Basic" with value "10"
When I select field label "Flex Direction" of header "Layout" with radio "row"
When I select field label "Direction" of header "Layout" with radio "ltr"
When I select field label "Flex Wrap" of header "Layout" with radio "nowrap"
When I select dropdown field label "Justify Content" of header "Layout" with value "center"
When I select dropdown field label "Align Items" of header "Layout" with value "flex-start"
When I select dropdown field label "Align Self" of header "Layout" with value "flex-end"
When I select field label "Position" of header "Position" with radio "absolute"
When I update field label "Top" of header "Position" with value "100"
When I update field label "Bottom" of header "Position" with value "100"
When I update field label "Left" of header "Position" with value "100"
When I update field label "Right" of header "Position" with value "100"
When I update field label "Top" of header "Margin" with value "10"
When I update field label "Bottom" of header "Margin" with value "10"
When I update field label "Left" of header "Margin" with value "10"
When I update field label "Right" of header "Margin" with value "10"
When I update field label "Top" of header "Padding" with value "10"
When I update field label "Bottom" of header "Padding" with value "10"
When I update field label "Left" of header "Padding" with value "10"
When I update field label "Right" of header "Padding" with value "10"
When I open preview code with style mode
Then I should see the code content "M1901_STYLE_TEXT"
